- cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms) is relevant as the paper discusses the use of spatial conjunction in reasoning about dynamically allocated data structures. 
- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is relevant as spatial conjunction can be used in reasoning about concurrent, distributed, and mobile computation. 
- cs.SE (Software Engineering) is less likely but still possible as the paper discusses the usefulness of spatial conjunction in reasoning about the contents of data structures in object-oriented languages, which is relevant to software engineering.
